{"hash":"64b5c7fea9f9a3b15639551b8e0e8ade56aa0e2b","data":{"post":{"title":"Remove a DOM Element in JavaScript","date":"June 20, 2020","content":"<p>Consider we have a <code>div</code> with 3 <code>span</code></p>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #292D3E\"><code><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">div</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">id</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">parent</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">span</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">id</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">child-1</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">1</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">span</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">span</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">id</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">child-2</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">2</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">span</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">span</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">id</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">child-3</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">3</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">span</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">div</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></code></pre>\n<p>To remove an element you can use <code>remove</code> method on the node</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #292D3E\"><code><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">let</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">child2</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">=</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> document</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">getElementById</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">child-2</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">)</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">child2</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">remove</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">()</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #676E95\">//removes the second span element</span></code></pre>\n<p>If we call <code>remove</code>  method on parent then all child node will also deleted along with <code>parent</code></p>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #292D3E\"><code><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">let</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">parent</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">=</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> document</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">getElementById</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">'</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">parent</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">'</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">)</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">parent</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">remove</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">()</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #676E95\">// deletes all node</span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"removing-body-of-the-webpage\"><a href=\"#removing-body-of-the-webpage\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Removing body of the webpage</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #292D3E\"><code><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">let</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">body</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">=</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> document</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">body</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">body</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">remove</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">()</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></code></pre>\n<hr>\n<p>Please donate <a href=\"https://www.paypal.me/jagathishSaravanan?locale.x=en_GB\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a>, for making more tutorials.</p>\n","tags":[{"title":"JavaScript","path":"/tag/JavaScript/"},{"title":"DOM","path":"/tag/DOM/"}]}},"context":{}}